  "data": {
    "title": "Unitel Voice Tutorial: Set Up a Pro Phone System in Minutes",
    "excerpt": "Step-by-step guide to setting up Unitel Voice for your small business. Get a professional number, IVR, and extensions without the hassle. Start today.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/how-to-use-unitel-voice.jpg",
        "alt": "Unitel Voice Tutorial: Set Up a Pro Phone System in Minutes",
        "filename": "how-to-use-unitel-voice.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You started your business to do what you love — not to waste hours figuring out phone systems that cost a fortune and require an IT degree to configure.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I get it. I've been there. Juggling client calls on my personal number, missing calls because I didn't know if it was a friend or a customer, and feeling like my one-person operation sounded like... well, a one-person operation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://unitelvoice.partnerlinks.io/6ukqdgxgwxld"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and everything changed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice is a virtual phone system built for people who are building businesses. It gives you a professional phone number, call forwarding, extensions, and a full IVR (Interactive Voice Response) menu — all manageable from your phone or laptop. No hardware. No contracts. No tech headaches.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "In this tutorial, I'll walk you through the exact steps to get your Unitel Voice system running in under 15 minutes. By the end, you'll sound like a company with a corner office — even if you're answering calls from your kitchen table.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Visit the Unitel Voice Website and Choose Your Plan",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://unitelvoice.com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Head over to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "unitelvoice.com",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and click on \"See Plans & Pricing.\" You'll see a handful of straightforward plans designed for different business sizes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what I love about their pricing: there are no hidden fees, no long-term contracts, and no surprises. Whether you're a solo freelancer or a team of ten, there's a plan that fits.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Take a minute to compare what each plan includes. The basics — like a business number and call forwarding — come standard across all tiers. Higher plans unlock features like additional extensions, more minutes, and advanced IVR options.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Start with the plan that matches your current needs. You can always upgrade later as your business grows. Unitel Voice scales with you, which is something I wish more services offered.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you've picked your plan, create your account. The signup process takes about two minutes. No lengthy forms, no credit check, no nonsense.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-unitel-voice"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want to explore the full breakdown of ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what Unitel Voice offers",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", we've got a deep dive on TonyCiencia that covers every feature in detail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Pick Your Perfect Business Phone Number",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the fun part.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After signing up, Unitel Voice prompts you to choose a phone number. You have options:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Local numbers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Pick an area code that matches your target market. If you serve customers in Austin, grab a 512 number. Building clientele in New York? Go with 212 or 646.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Toll-free numbers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Want to project a bigger presence? A 1-800 or 1-888 number says \"we're established\" before you even say hello.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Vanity numbers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Think 1-800-FLOWERS, but for your business. These are memorable and brandable.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I went with a local number for my area because most of my clients are regional. But if you serve customers nationally, toll-free is the way to go.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The search tool is fast — type in your preferred area code or keyword, and Unitel Voice shows you what's available in seconds. Lock in your number, and you're officially in business.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One thing that impressed me:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You don't need a second phone. Unitel Voice works on top of your existing cell phone. Your personal number stays private, and your business calls come through on a separate line. It's that clean.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Set Up Call Forwarding So You Never Miss a Call",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's where Unitel Voice really shines for busy entrepreneurs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call forwarding is the backbone of the system. It routes incoming business calls to any phone you want — your cell, your home office landline, your partner's phone, or even a team member across the country.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "To set it up:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Log into your Unitel Voice dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Navigate to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call Forwarding",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " settings.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Enter the phone number(s) where you want calls to ring.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Choose your ring order — simultaneous (all phones ring at once) or sequential (ring one, then the next if no answer).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's it. Three minutes, tops.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have my calls ring my cell first. If I don't pick up after four rings, it rolls to my business partner's phone. If neither of us answers, it goes to voicemail. Customers always reach someone — or at least get a professional voicemail greeting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This feature alone transformed how I handle my workday. I can step away from my desk, run errands, or travel, and my business phone follows me. No missed leads. No frustrated customers. No stress.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/unitel-voice-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to learn more tricks for getting the most out of Unitel Voice? Check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "tips and best practices guide",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for insider strategies.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Build Your IVR Menu (Auto-Attendant)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the feature that makes your one-person business sound like a corporation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "An IVR — Interactive Voice Response — is that professional greeting callers hear when they dial your number. You know the ones: \"Press 1 for sales, press 2 for support, press 3 for billing.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "With Unitel Voice, building an IVR is drag-and-drop simple. Here's how:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Go to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Auto-Attendant",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " in your dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Record or upload your greeting. (You can use your own voice, or use a text-to-speech option for a polished tone.)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Set up menu options. For example:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "   - Press 1 → Rings your cell",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "   - Press 2 → Goes to sales voicemail",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "   - Press 3 → Plays business hours and address",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Assign each option to a destination — a phone number, an extension, a voicemail box, or an informational message.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can create multiple layers, too. Press 1, then hear another menu with sub-options. It's flexible enough to handle complex routing but simple enough that you won't need a tutorial to build the tutorial.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When I set up my IVR, I kept it minimal: \"Thanks for calling [Business Name]. Press 1 for new inquiries, press 2 for existing clients, or hold for the next available person.\" It took me five minutes, and clients regularly compliment how professional it sounds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/unitel-voice-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a closer look at all the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "new features Unitel Voice has rolled out recently",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", TonyCiencia has you covered.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Add Extensions for Your Team",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Growing your team? Unitel Voice makes it painless to add extensions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Each team member gets their own extension number. When a caller presses a menu option or dials an extension, the call routes directly to that person's phone — wherever they are.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the setup:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Go to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Extensions",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " in your dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Click ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Add Extension",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Enter the team member's name and the phone number where they'll receive calls.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Assign an extension number (like 101, 102, etc.).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Optionally, set a custom voicemail greeting for that extension.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Now your IVR can say, \"Press 1 to reach John, press 2 to reach Sarah,\" and the system handles the routing automatically. John could be in his home office in Denver. Sarah could be at a client site in Miami. The caller doesn't know — and doesn't need to. They just hear a professional, organized operation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I added my first team extension six months after signing up. The process took under two minutes, and it immediately leveled up how my business communicated.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
