          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New & Standout Features You'll Appreciate",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice isn't standing still — they keep adding features that make the platform even more useful for business builders. Here are some highlights:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Mobile app management",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Control your entire phone system from your smartphone. Change forwarding rules, check voicemail, update your IVR — all from the app.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Voicemail-to-email",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Get voicemails delivered straight to your inbox as audio files. Listen on the go, forward to a teammate, or save for records.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call analytics",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — See how many calls you're getting, when they come in, and how long they last. Data-driven decisions for your communication strategy.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Business hours routing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Set different call handling for business hours vs. after hours. During the day, calls ring your phone. After 6 PM, they go to a custom voicemail or an informational message.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Custom greetings",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Record professional greetings for your main line, extensions, and voicemail boxes. First impressions matter, and Unitel Voice helps you nail them every time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Multiple phone numbers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Need separate numbers for different departments, campaigns, or regions? Add them all under one account.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "These aren't gimmicks. They're practical tools that save time, reduce chaos, and make your business look polished from the very first ring.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
