      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Unitel Voice Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice isn't trying to be everything for everyone — and that's a strength. It's purpose-built for specific types of business builders who need a reliable, affordable phone system without the bloat.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Freelancers and solopreneurs",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If you're wearing every hat in your business, Unitel Voice gives you a professional phone presence without adding complexity. One number, forwarded to your cell, with a voicemail greeting that makes you sound established.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small business owners with growing teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Adding employees? Extensions and multi-user routing keep everyone connected under one business number. No need for separate phone plans.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remote and hybrid teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Your team doesn't need to be in the same building — or even the same time zone. Unitel Voice routes calls to wherever your people are.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Service-based businesses",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Plumbers, consultants, real estate agents, coaches, agencies — anyone who relies on phone calls to book clients and close deals benefits from a system that ensures no call goes unanswered.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Side hustlers scaling up",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Still using your personal number for your side gig? Unitel Voice is the bridge between \"side project\" and \"real business.\" It costs less than most streaming subscriptions and delivers ten times the value.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-commerce brands",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Even if most of your sales happen online, having a professional phone number builds trust. Customers feel more confident buying from a business they can actually call.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Basically, if phone calls matter to your business — and they almost certainly do — Unitel Voice is worth every penny.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
