        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "My Final Take: Why I Recommend Unitel Voice",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested a lot of business tools. Some are overpriced. Some are overcomplicated. Some promise the world and deliver a headache.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l7",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://unitelvoice.partnerlinks.io/6ukqdgxgwxld"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Get started with Unitel Voice today",
            "marks": [
              "l7"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see the difference for yourself.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice is none of those things. It's refreshingly simple, genuinely affordable, and packed with the exact features small business owners actually need. No fluff. No \"enterprise\" pricing for basic functionality. No three-week setup process.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You sign up. You pick a number. You set up forwarding and an IVR. You sound professional. Done.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The fact that you can do all of this from your phone, in under fifteen minutes, while sitting at a coffee shop or waiting for your kid's soccer practice to end — that's the kind of tool I want in my corner.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're tired of giving out your personal number, missing calls because your phone was on silent, or feeling like your business doesn't \"sound\" as legit as it is, Unitel Voice solves all of that. One subscription. One dashboard. Total control.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
