        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need a second phone to use Unitel Voice?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No. Unitel Voice works on top of your existing cell phone. Business calls come through your current device, keeping your personal number completely separate and private.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How long does it take to set up Unitel Voice?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most users are fully set up in under 15 minutes. Signing up takes about two minutes, choosing a number takes another minute, and configuring call forwarding and an IVR takes roughly ten more.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I add team members to my Unitel Voice account?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. You can add extensions for each team member, routing calls directly to their individual phones regardless of location. Setup takes under two minutes per extension.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Unitel Voice offer toll-free numbers?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. You can choose from local numbers, toll-free numbers (1-800, 1-888, etc.), and even vanity numbers to match your brand. All available during the signup process.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
